Class ServiceName

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.co.visalia.brightpearl.apiclient.ServiceName

  • public final class ServiceName
extends Object
    An extendable enum containing the known Brightpearl services and allowing a custom service name to be used. Used to create requests.
